   281â†’### Function Schemas
   321â†’## Streaming
   336â†’# Evaluations
   338â†’Evaluations are crucial to any project, and we encourage developers to bring their own eval suites to test the performance of their swarms. For reference, we have some examples for how to eval swarm in the `airline`, `weather_agent` and `triage_agent` quickstart examples. See the READMEs for more details.
   339â†’
   340â†’# Utils
   342â†’Use the `run_demo_loop` to test out your swarm! This will run a REPL on your command line. Supports streaming.
   343â†’
   344â†’```python
   345â†’from swarm.repl import run_demo_loop
   346â†’...
   347â†’run_demo_loop(agent, stream=True)
   348â†’```
   349â†’
