     1â†’# Airline customer service
     3â†’This example demonstrates a multi-agent setup for handling different customer service requests in an airline context using the Swarm framework. The agents can triage requests, handle flight modifications, cancellations, and lost baggage cases.
     4â†’This example uses the helper function `run_demo_loop`, which allows us to create an interactive Swarm session.
